# qodana-go — Qodana Ultimate for Go/GoLand (image name = repoName). Feed code QDGO. Internal nightly
# dist feed: unsigned tar.gz, sha256-only (no GPG .asc), eap; the build mounts
# QODANA_READ_SPACE_PACKAGES_TOKEN (compose.private.yaml). Builds on the DHI golang language base
# (Go PRE-BAKED, but NO node), so — unlike qodana-js's node base — it LAYERS the node toolchain
# (NODE_MAJOR) + the in-place eslint pin for JS/TS support, exactly like the source qodana-cli
# go.Dockerfile. SAME key set as qodana-jvm (dist + node toolchain). NO DIST_BASE_STAGE (node+eslint are
# in-place on base; the dist FROMs base). The golang base does NOT occupy uid 1000 (empirically:
# /etc/passwd has only root/nonroot/_apt/nobody), so qodana-go keeps base.dockerfile's DEFAULT uid 1000
# and sets NO uid keys/build args — only qodana-js needs the 1001 shift. eslint is pinned in
# lib/toolchain/eslint/package.json (renovate-tracked), NOT here. Pins in docs/phase-0-decisions.md;
# EnvContractTest asserts byte-identity for QD_VERSION/QD_BUILD/QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE + the feed/verify/eap
# contract and the golang base digest.
QD_LINTER_SLUG=qodana-go
QD_VERSION=2026.3
# renovate: datasource=custom.qodana-dist depName=qodana-go versioning=loose
QD_BUILD=262.5912.2297
QD_DISTRIBUTION_FEED=https://packages.jetbrains.team/files/p/sa/qodana-dist-internal/feed
QD_VERIFY_MODE=sha256
QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE=GO
QD_BASE_IMAGE=dhi.io/golang:1.26-debian13-dev@sha256:d1295e34ae659bfd57c305d67ec5177c15694fb82f25d98aee76d0ae08ef8ad1
CLI_BINARY=qodana
CLI_VERSION=2026.2
CLI_OS=linux
NODE_MAJOR=20
